title: Statement from President Joe Biden and First Lady Jill Biden on the Retirement of United States Secret Service Director Jim Murray | The White House
content: Director Jim Murray has led a long and distinguished career in federal and military service for three decades, including the last three years as Director of the United States Secret Service.Â Jim embodies the meaning of service over self, and protected the families of U.S. Presidents like they were part of his own. We are incredibly grateful for his service to our country and our family.###
